window.bookSummaryJSON = "What happens when the very gods depend on mortals for help? That's what three very different young women find out when they are invited to Warrior's Peak. <p>Light and Knowledge have succeeded in their quest, and two of the keys have been found. The final, and last, test goes to Zoe McCourt - Valor.</p> <p>Zoe has the courage to raise her young son alone, and to face all the adversity life has thrown at them. But will she have the courage to face a foe determined to do anything to stop the third key from being found - even destroying everything and everyone she loves?</p>"; 
